{"tid":1047870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★HK No IT】始創中心需騰空樓層for處理$4000，屋宇署需搬遷","createTime":"2019-03-05T09:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T13:40:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"50209176b4749015ec98e3c1ec5e24518ee381c3","tid":1047870,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:04:07.000Z","msg":"屋宇署趕入伙，是否為了騰空太子的辦公室讓部門處理「派四千蚊」，產業署無正面回覆，只表示相關部門搬離後騰出的租用物業，該署會跟進退租或重新編配事宜。政府發言人指，關愛共享計劃於今年二月一日開始接受申請，預計最多三百萬人符合該計劃的申請資格，為推行計劃，職津處需設置辦事處，以處理申請。職津處已於今年一月底接收旺角始創中心十五及十六樓，並會於下月初接收十四樓及十七樓。<br />\n<br />\n議員轟安排離譜 應無縫交接<br />\n立法會議員柯創盛批評政府安排離譜，派發四千元事件討論多時，不應急急安排辦公室等事宜，認為規劃者嚴重失職，亦無體諒員工苦況及安全，「七宗罪都未搞掂就遷入，過程中有部門失職，正常應該可以做到無縫交接」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190304/00174_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190304%2F00174_001.html&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=4689035b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190304/00174_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a9e4a910ef3bdacb1b652665742311335328698d","tid":1047870,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3613baade11189a251f9efd3ecf9afa63300ba4","tid":1047870,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/172814_283c4147a0ce7919c3023935c89ebaef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F172814_283c4147a0ce7919c3023935c89ebaef.png&h=4dd0c097&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14a8a86569628a3a05270cc1e5cd2f1a7a6e2b84","tid":1047870,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14cbf8